[[File:Yeonpyeong_shelling.png|thumb]]
据报道，21日金正恩视察了该地区的炮兵部队（炮战“金正恩式打击”）。2010年11月23日上午10時，韩国在[[延坪島|延坪島]]附近海域上進行已預定年度例行的軍事砲擊演習。當日，北韓曾要求韓國停止有關軍事演習并宣称说不会容忍对自己领海的炮击，<ref>{{cite news |title=Military to kick off annual defense drill next week |first= |last= |publisher=YonHap News Agency |date=2010-11-16 |url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2010/11/16/10/0301000000AEN20101116007000315F.HTML |accessdate=2010-11-27 |archive-date=2016-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228224754/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/national/2010/11/16/10/0301000000AEN20101116007000315F.HTML }}</ref>但韩国方面不予理會，并向韩国一方的水域进行了发射炮弹的演习，<ref name=koreaherald-20101123>Sang-ho, Song. "[http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?newsMLId=20101123000840 North Korea fires artillery into sea near western border] {{Wayback|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/national/Detail.jsp?newsMLId=20101123000840 |date=20120320090446 }}." ''The Korea Herald'', 2010-11-23</ref>据一名韩国军官称，演习发射的炮弹是避开朝鲜而偏向南发射的。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2010-11-23-korea-artillery_N.htm|date=2010-11-23|accessdate=2010-11-25|author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|title=N. Korea fires artillery onto S. Korean island; 2 dead|quote=During the drills, South Korean marines on the island shot artillery toward southern waters, away from North Korea, the official said.|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426094518/http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2010-11-23-korea-artillery_N.htm}}</ref>岛上驻扎的[[韓國海軍陸戰隊|韓國海軍陸戰隊]]上校说是向西南方向发射<ref>{{cite news|author=Jack Kim|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|title=South Korean military defends response to attack|date=2010-11-25|quote="North Korea argues that we fired at them first, but this is the direction that we fired," he said standing on the northern tip of the normally idyllic island of fishermen, pointing southwest, away from North Korea.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/08/10/world/asia/10korea.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-05-25 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621074334/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/08/10/world/asia/10korea.html }}</ref>。

在当日时间下午约2點34分，[[朝鮮人民軍|朝鮮人民軍]]開始向韓國延坪島炮兵陣地射擊。延坪島上的韓國軍事設施隨即在砲擊中起火，南韓方面立刻用[[K-9自行火炮|K-9自行火炮]]（六辆中共有四辆正常开火）向朝鲜海岸炮部队基地還擊。朝鮮遭到韓國還擊後，隨即又進行了還擊。朝鲜的砲擊造成延坪島上多處居民区[[停電|停電]]与[[火灾|火灾]]，据朝鲜叛逃者说共发射了108发。

韓國的砲擊也造成了朝鮮方面的損失。南韓軍方命令疏散平民躲進[[防空洞|防空洞]]內<ref>{{Cite news |title= N.Korea shells S.Korea island, 4 troops wounded |url= http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5gDK7k9zXOEF0hiuQbIDAQrk-_LVA?docId=CNG.a36c20fecf84254d28bd7d6b22adfb1e.8e1 |agency= [[Agence_France-Presse|AFP]] |publisher= [[Google|Google]] |date= November 23, 2010 |accessdate= November 23, 2010 |archive-date= 2012-05-27 |archive-url= https://archive.is/20120527081359/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5gDK7k9zXOEF0hiuQbIDAQrk-_LVA?docId=CNG.a36c20fecf84254d28bd7d6b22adfb1e.8e1 |dead-url= no }}}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title= South Koreans hurt, evacuated after North Korea firing |url= http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6AM0W920101123 |agency= [[Reuters|Reuters]] |date= November 23, 2010 |accessdate= November 23, 2010 |archive-date= 2010-11-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101126154351/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6AM0W920101123 }}</ref><ref name=hjf>{{Cite web |url=http://cnnews.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/11/25/20101125000005.html |title=韩军方：未能直接回射北韩海岸炮，朝鮮日報中文網，2010年11月25日 |access-date=2015年4月27日 |archive-date=2016年3月5日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305062605/http://cnnews.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/11/25/20101125000005.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，且快速重新組織在島上的戰力，並迅速派遣[[F-15K|F-15K]]、[[F-16|F-16]]戰鬥機協防空域<ref name=hjf/>。

